1981;;Death of a Centerfold: The Dorothy Stratten Story;;American;;Gabrielle Beaumont;;Jamie Lee Curtis, Bruce Weitz, Robert Reed;;biography;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Death_of_a_Centerfold:_The_Dorothy_Stratten_Story;;A depiction of the life and times of an up and coming model and actress, Dorothy Stratten, a 20-year old playboy playmate, who's life is tragically cut short when she becomes involved with and marries a shady man, Paul Snider, who later kills her in a murder-suicide.